            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Variáveis podem conter todos os tipos de valores. Vamos dar uma olhada em armazenar valores de texto, como <code>\"Porsche\"</code> aqui.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"car_1 = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Porsche&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"text\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"Porsche\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Giving a variable a value",
            "id": 123583,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Depois de criar e nomear uma variável, usamos o sinal <code>=</code> para armazenar um <strong>valor</strong> dentro dela.</p><p>Digite <code>=</code> para armazenar o valor <code>\"Miami\"</code> dentro da variável <code>city</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"city = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Miami&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"5\" endIndex=\"6\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Storing",
            "id": 123586,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Armazenar um valor em uma variável é como colocar coisas dentro de uma caixa rotulada. Aqui, a variável <code>device_type</code> armazena o valor <code>\"apple\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"device_type = \" /><text value=\"&quot;apple&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"12\" endIndex=\"13\" /><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"21\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>=</code> seguido de <code>\"apple\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "String",
            "id": 123585,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Os valores que temos armazenado, como <code>\"Miami\"</code>, são <strong>strings</strong>. Valores de string são textos entre aspas duplas.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"city = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Miami&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"7\" endIndex=\"8\" /><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\".\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\".\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"</code> seguido de <code>\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
