            "title": "Displaying multiple times",
            "id": 75989,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos usar a instrução <code>print()</code> quantas vezes quisermos. O computador exibe cada valor em uma nova linha no console.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;3, 2, 1&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;GO!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option startIndex=\"28\" endIndex=\"29\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"3, 2, 1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"GO!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>print</code> seguido de <code>(</code> e finalmente <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
